PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772463771
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'selfless and
OL,4,Cfearless' war photographer Paul Conroy
OL,6,FThe circumstances leading up to the
OL,7,Fattack, which left Colvin and
OL,8,Fphotographer Remi Ochlik dead and
OL,9,FConroy injured, was later the subject
OL,10,Fof a film starring Jamie Dornan.
OL,12,FSyrian journalist Fared Al Mahlool
OL,13,Fsaid: "I am heartbroken to share the
OL,14,Fdevastating news of the death of my
OL,15,Fdear friend, Paul Conroy.
OL,17,F"Paul died of a heart attack. He did
OL,18,Fnot hesitate. He faced his final
OL,19,Fmoments with courage and dignity.
OL,26,@pD@Orr
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772463771
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'selfless and
OL,4,Cfearless' war photographer Paul Conroy
OL,6,F"He died a hero - selfless, fearless,
OL,7,Fand deeply human. My heart is
OL,8,Fshattered. Rest in peace, Paul. You
OL,9,Fwill never be forgotten."
OL,11,FConroy, from Totnes, Devon, had
OL,12,Fcontinued working after recovering
OL,13,Ffrom the 2012 attack and turned his
OL,14,Fattention to Ukraine following the
OL,15,FRussian invasion in 2022.
OL,17,FKyiv-based correspondent Oz Katerji
OL,18,Fwrote: "I am devastated to learn that
OL,19,Fmy dear friend, my brother in arms,
OL,20,FPaul Conroy has gone on to the next
OL,21,Flife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772463771
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'selfless and
OL,4,Cfearless' war photographer Paul Conroy
OL,6,F"He was one of the bravest men I have
OL,7,Fever known. I can barely believe it,
OL,8,Fwe only spoke yesterday.
OL,10,F"His loss will be felt profoundly by
OL,11,Fus all."
OL,13,FConroy co-wrote a song with Joss Stone
OL,14,Fin support of Amnesty International
OL,15,Fafter the pair met when the singer
OL,16,Fmade a documentary at the age of 15.
OL,18,FWar footage he filmed was used in the
OL,19,Fsingle's video.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
