PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1772463771
OL,3,CTributes paid to 'selfless and
OL,4,Cfearless' war photographer Paul Conroy
OL,6,FWriting on Facebook, she said: "I
OL,7,Fwouldn't be the person I am today with
OL,8,Fout Paul.
OL,10,F"Paul Conroy was a legend. A wonderful
OL,11,Fperson through and through. Always
OL,12,Fstanding up for what was right. Always
OL,13,Fthere for those in need."
OL,15,FFriend and BBC presenter Clive Myrie
OL,16,Fsaid he was "utterly devastated" at
OL,17,Fthe news about Conroy's death and
OL,18,Fdescribed him as a "wonderful
OL,19,Fphotojournalist and a wonderful human
OL,20,Fbeing".
OL,26,@xD@`O]
