OL,3,CTributes paid to 'selfless and
OL,4,Cfearless' war photographer Paul Conroy
OL,6,FLindsey Hilsum, Channel 4 News
OL,7,FInternational Editor, said on X that
OL,8,FConroy was visiting family in Devon at
OL,9,Fthe time of his death.
OL,11,F"All of us who knew and loved him are
OL,12,Fdevastated," she added.
